These days I've been busy programming a version of Lavaurs algorithm for the
idenfication of circle chords: the abstract Mandelbrot set.

The images don't look like much, but the output of the program is nicer: it
outputs an Encapsulated PostScript file which looks sharper. But when converting
to `png` with ImageMagick some distortion appeared.

